==[[Sumerian]]==
===Etymology===
Compound of '''''nam''''' (abstract prefix) + '''''dub<sub>3</sub>''''' (''du<sub>10</sub>'', gladness) + '''''sa''''' (to repay).

===Noun===
'''namdubsa''' (nam-dub3-sa)

# [[companionship]], [[friendship]]

